<paragraph id="373EDC396D3955B1C1BBE362F7320B96" pageId="0" pageNumber="93">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A868488D61D4865F296638337FE8D949" pageId="0" pageNumber="93">
<taxonomicName id="F6E64743D85BA7E83598C5B24B8635AC" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Lachemilla" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Lachemilla rothmaleriana" order="Rosales" pageId="0" pageNumber="93" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rothmaleriana">
<emphasis id="419C080B8A1F08CFF795044995962684" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="93">Lachemilla rothmaleriana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<taxonomicName id="1B461548D4D8F500DF08E93A1EA09173" class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Rosaceae" genus="L." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="L. hispidula" order="Rosales" pageId="0" pageNumber="93" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="hispidula">
<emphasis id="71B05BB2294DE5FFBDC41DDBEC2AD89C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="93">L. hispidula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(L.M. Perry) Rothm. and 
<taxonomicName id="50927E8241E4541CDF351A9EC84AB012" class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Rosaceae" genus="L." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="L. nivalis" order="Rosales" pageId="0" pageNumber="93" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="nivalis">
<emphasis id="0CD5796855DA3C5DD3DA2E11105CF1B8" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="93">L. nivalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Kunth) Rothm. by its stout stems, sericeous-villous indumentum, wide ascending sheaths with trilobate lateral lobes, and a turbinate-campanulate hypanthium.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
